## 24. Senior Developer Notes

> [!WARNING]
> Do not change row and column mapping indices in Python files without validating the spreadsheet templates. Excel formulas are mapped to exact cell coordinates.

- **Formula Rewriting**: `stage4_attainment.py` copies formulas from Sheet1 to Sheet2 and adds the `Sheet1!` prefix. If you modify Sheet1's layout, make sure to update `src_start` in the python script.
- **Excel Cell Formats**: If cells are read as string formulas instead of evaluated float values, the calculation scripts will fail. Always load workbooks with `data_only=True` when reading values, and `data_only=False` when modifying cells with formulas.

